	<strong>Burial Options</strong></p>
<p>
	Ivy Lawn Memorial Park offers a wide range of burial options.</p>
<p>
	Choose from a variety of settings, sizes, and price points. Whatever you select, your purchase includes “endowment care” which provides perpetual maintenance of basics like grass cover and care of a crypt or niche. For an additional fee, we can arrange ongoing planting, monument upkeep, and flower arrangements.</p>
<p>
	Have more questions? We invite you to contact our staff or attend one of our programs about burial and other end-of-life concerns. These scheduled events include walking tours of new burial space and talks by estate lawyers, funeral directors and other experts.</p>
