	<strong>Products</strong></p>
<p>
	Our cemetery reflects Ivy Lawn’s reputation for quality, craftsmanship, and care, encompassing the cemetery’s historic entrance, cremation gardens, niches, crypts, chapel, and mausoleums.</p>
<p>
	To address the national trend toward cremation, a large number of spaces for cremated remains are available. Granite benches are located throughout the setting. Prices range from $2,000 - $ 7,000.</p>
<p>
	Ivy Lawn’s memorials spaces fulfill and respond to today’s evolving needs for burial and commemoration.</p>
<p>
	Our burial options allow for casket burial, urn burial, and burial of cremated remains without an urn. In addition, a number of garden burials with individual markers are available, as well as burials with upright monuments.</p>
